üí° Core Value of the Video Contest System

The Video Contest feature is where Flixbit blends marketing + gamification + user rewards.
It gives users a reason to return daily, helps sellers advertise creatively, and allows Admins to monitor meaningful engagement while driving platform revenue through Flixbit transactions.